Class BoundedTaskExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.AbstractExecutorService
      • com.intellij.util.concurrency.BoundedTaskExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.concurrent.Executor, java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService

    public final class BoundedTaskExecutor
extends java.util.concurrent.AbstractExecutorService
    ExecutorService which limits the number of tasks running simultaneously. The number of submitted tasks is unrestricted.
